00:00:51.542 --> 00:00:53.250 align:middle line:84%
>>PATTI NEGRI: Yes,
yes, I've been lucky.

00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:55.920 align:middle line:84%
I guess I'm an LA
native, born and raised

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:56.840 align:middle line:90%
in the Hollywood area.

00:00:56.840 --> 00:00:58.095 align:middle line:84%
