with the territory.

00:00:58.095 --> 00:00:59.845 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How did you
get involved in this?

00:00:59.845 --> 00:01:02.250 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: I-- well, a
long and windy road.

00:01:02.250 --> 00:01:06.330 align:middle line:10%
I knew when I was a little kid
that those imaginary friends

00:01:06.330 --> 00:01:08.370 align:middle line:10%
little kids have
weren't all imaginary.

00:01:08.370 --> 00:01:10.080 align:middle line:10%
I could talk to spirits.

00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:12.672 align:middle line:10%
And then I also kind of
went into the showbiz realm,

00:01:12.672 --> 00:01:14.130 align:middle line:10%
and then one day
they all collided.

00:01:14.130 --> 00:01:17.763 align:middle line:90%


00:01:17.763 --> 00:01:18.930 align:middle line:90%
I ran a production company--

00:01:18.930 --> 00:01:19.730 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: OK.

00:01:19.730 --> 00:01:22.265 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: And I just--

00:01:22.265 --> 00:01:24.390 align:middle line:84%
I stayed away, even though
I talked to dead people,

00:01:24.390 --> 00:01:26.460 align:middle line:84%
even though I was a
witch and I did magic.

00:01:26.460 --> 00:01:28.650 align:middle line:84%
I thought that wasn't
proper if I was doing

00:01:28.650 --> 00:01:30.210 align:middle line:90%
big shows for Mattel and IBM.

00:01:30.210 --> 00:01:31.200 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Scare people.

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:34.980 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, yes, but
one day, like in 2008,

00:01:34.980 --> 00:01:36.497 align:middle line:84%
when kind of the
corporate market

00:01:36.497 --> 00:01:38.580 align:middle line:84%
dropped out of corporate
entertainment and reality

00:01:38.580 --> 00:01:40.140 align:middle line:84%
television was
going up like this,

00:01:40.140 --> 00:01:42.900 align:middle line:84%
I kind of came out of the
proverbial broom closet.

00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:46.320 align:middle line:84%
Somebody had asked me to
do a show on, I think,

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.210 align:middle line:90%
"Mobile Home Disaster" on CMT.

00:01:48.210 --> 00:01:49.860 align:middle line:84%
I'm like, well, nobody
will watch that.

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:51.870 align:middle line:90%
I could do that show.

00:01:51.870 --> 00:01:54.240 align:middle line:84%
And people did watch
it and it didn't

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:57.480 align:middle line:84%
hurt my corporate career, though
this career turned into where

00:01:57.480 --> 00:01:58.620 align:middle line:90%
my passion really lies.

00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:00.865 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And this is basically
your full-time career.

00:02:00.865 --> 00:02:02.490 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: This my full
time career, yes.

00:02:02.490 --> 00:02:05.032 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Casting spells, doing
all kinds of things on people.

00:02:05.032 --> 00:02:07.959 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Casting spells,
working with people, seances,

00:02:07.959 --> 00:02:08.759 align:middle line:90%
a lot of house--

00:02:08.759 --> 00:02:09.900 align:middle line:90%
I see energy.

00:02:09.900 --> 00:02:11.790 align:middle line:84%
I do-- everything
is energy-based and

00:02:11.790 --> 00:02:13.080 align:middle line:90%
empowerment-based.

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:16.860 align:middle line:84%
So whether I'm getting the
ghost of Aaron Spelling out

00:02:16.860 --> 00:02:20.310 align:middle line:84%
of Spelling Manor, or helping
a little beauty shop that

00:02:20.310 --> 00:02:24.140 align:middle line:84%
doesn't know why they can't keep
clients and clearing it out,

00:02:24.140 --> 00:02:26.100 align:middle line:90%
or everywhere in the middle.

00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:29.070 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Patti, is
your gift inherited?

00:02:29.070 --> 00:02:30.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I think it's inherited.

00:02:30.540 --> 00:02:33.775 align:middle line:84%
When I was little, my mom always
said, oh, grandma, did that.

00:02:33.775 --> 00:02:36.150 align:middle line:84%
Grandma was able to talk to
people at the end of the bed,

00:02:36.150 --> 00:02:36.450 align:middle line:90%
too.

00:02:36.450 --> 00:02:38.070 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's
because my father had

00:02:38.070 --> 00:02:40.950 align:middle line:84%
this Sephardic
Jewish background.

00:02:40.950 --> 00:02:42.750 align:middle line:84%
But we were raised--
my grandfather

00:02:42.750 --> 00:02:45.310 align:middle line:90%
was this very famous atheist.

00:02:45.310 --> 00:02:47.070 align:middle line:84%
He hung out with Carl
Sagan, academic--

00:02:47.070 --> 00:02:48.000 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, he did?

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.820 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: --and it is like
anything religious or spiritual

00:02:50.820 --> 00:02:52.680 align:middle line:90%
was a dirty word to me.

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:55.890 align:middle line:84%
So I wasn't raised with
any kind of spirituality.

00:02:55.890 --> 00:02:57.930 align:middle line:84%
But I would pass a
church, or I would

00:02:57.930 --> 00:03:00.600 align:middle line:84%
pass a temple or a synagogue,
and I'd see this energy,

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:02.830 align:middle line:90%
and I'd just want to know more.

00:03:02.830 --> 00:03:06.060 align:middle line:84%
So I think I was 13 by the time
I said, can I go to church?

00:03:06.060 --> 00:03:08.980 align:middle line:84%
Can I-- and my mom's like, you
could do anything you want.

00:03:08.980 --> 00:03:10.320 align:middle line:90%
And thus, a seeker was born.

00:03:10.320 --> 00:03:13.380 align:middle line:84%
And I just went everywhere
and learned everything,

00:03:13.380 --> 00:03:16.050 align:middle line:84%
and took it all down to that
one similarity of the energy.

00:03:16.050 --> 00:03:17.940 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Sounds like
your mother was very

00:03:17.940 --> 00:03:19.237 align:middle line:90%
supportive of what you did.

00:03:19.237 --> 00:03:21.570 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: They've always been
very, very supportive, yes.

00:03:21.570 --> 00:03:21.960 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's good.

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:23.930 align:middle line:84%
You look like a younger
version of Barbra Streisand.

00:03:23.930 --> 00:03:24.280 align:middle line:90%
You ever get that?

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:25.410 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Oh, thank you.

00:03:25.410 --> 00:03:27.270 align:middle line:84%
No, but I'll take that
as a huge compliment.

00:03:27.270 --> 00:03:27.750 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Can you sing?

00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:28.385 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: No.

00:03:28.385 --> 00:03:29.130 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, you can't.

00:03:29.130 --> 00:03:31.047 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: It's the one
thing I really don't do.

00:03:31.047 --> 00:03:32.550 align:middle line:90%
I've done it a lot, weirdly.

00:03:32.550 --> 00:03:36.240 align:middle line:84%
I even got my SAG card
singing in "Rocky III."

00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:37.980 align:middle line:90%
Because I'm queen of--

00:03:37.980 --> 00:03:39.780 align:middle line:84%
because I'm a good
witch, I guess, I

00:03:39.780 --> 00:03:41.250 align:middle line:90%
can do things that I can't do.

00:03:41.250 --> 00:03:43.410 align:middle line:84%
I can't boil water and I
made it on "Master Chef."

00:03:43.410 --> 00:03:44.210 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Uh-huh.

00:03:44.210 --> 00:03:47.790 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: But my singing has to
be kind of character singing

00:03:47.790 --> 00:03:49.400 align:middle line:84%
because I slide off
key a little bit.

00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:50.490 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You're
a psychic medium.

00:03:50.490 --> 00:03:51.290 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yeah.

00:03:51.290 --> 00:03:54.171 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now tell me
exactly what you do there.

00:03:54.171 --> 00:03:55.980 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Well, on
the psychic side,

00:03:55.980 --> 00:03:57.510 align:middle line:90%
you just kind of know things.

00:03:57.510 --> 00:03:58.230 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You're
intuitive about that?

00:03:58.230 --> 00:03:59.188 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I'm intuitive.

00:03:59.188 --> 00:04:01.410 align:middle line:84%
I'm intuitive and I kind
of see more trajectory.

00:04:01.410 --> 00:04:03.327 align:middle line:84%
I'm not going to
ever tell somebody,

00:04:03.327 --> 00:04:05.160 align:middle line:84%
you're going to get hit
by a bus on Tuesday.

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:07.870 align:middle line:84%
Because number one, nothing
is written in stone.

00:04:07.870 --> 00:04:09.000 align:middle line:90%
We have free will.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.830 align:middle line:84%
And I could say be
careful on Tuesday,

00:04:10.830 --> 00:04:12.735 align:middle line:84%
and then you won't
get hit by a bus.

00:04:12.735 --> 00:04:14.070 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You do warn them.

00:04:14.070 --> 00:04:15.380 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I do warn them.

00:04:15.380 --> 00:04:19.170 align:middle line:84%
Just like, you might not be
paying attention to things.

00:04:19.170 --> 00:04:20.920 align:middle line:90%
But I am much bigger--

00:04:20.920 --> 00:04:23.580 align:middle line:84%
especially the witch side of
me, of that free will and we

00:04:23.580 --> 00:04:26.310 align:middle line:84%
create our own fate
over what we are given.

00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:27.420 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Interesting.

00:04:27.420 --> 00:04:28.270 align:middle line:90%
And the medium portion of that?

00:04:28.270 --> 00:04:30.062 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: The mediumship
is that the talking

00:04:30.062 --> 00:04:31.650 align:middle line:90%
to dead people and spirits.

00:04:31.650 --> 00:04:35.990 align:middle line:84%
I really-- I thought
everybody could.

00:04:35.990 --> 00:04:37.350 align:middle line:90%
I just thought it was normal.

00:04:37.350 --> 00:04:39.040 align:middle line:90%
I was three or four, or five.

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.950 align:middle line:90%
And I had my friends and I had--

00:04:40.950 --> 00:04:42.858 align:middle line:90%
I would astral project.

00:04:42.858 --> 00:04:44.400 align:middle line:84%
I would tell my
mom-- she'd be going,

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:46.742 align:middle line:84%
we're going to go meet the
Joneses for the first time.

00:04:46.742 --> 00:04:48.450 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, oh, I
was there last night.

00:04:48.450 --> 00:04:50.400 align:middle line:84%
She's like, you were
not there last night.

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:50.660 align:middle line:90%
And I--

00:04:50.660 --> 00:04:50.800 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Ha!

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:51.630 align:middle line:90%
Yes, I was, mom.

00:04:51.630 --> 00:04:54.060 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, I'd explain
every room in their house

00:04:54.060 --> 00:04:56.010 align:middle line:90%
and the color of the wallpaper.

00:04:56.010 --> 00:05:00.150 align:middle line:84%
And I always had this obsession,
but not in a dark or morbid

00:05:00.150 --> 00:05:01.740 align:middle line:90%
way, for the dead.

00:05:01.740 --> 00:05:04.650 align:middle line:84%
So I literally did my first
seance, I was seven or eight,

00:05:04.650 --> 00:05:07.620 align:middle line:84%
and my little suburban
Long Beach-area home.

00:05:07.620 --> 00:05:12.060 align:middle line:84%
I went into my windowless
hall and stuffed towels

00:05:12.060 --> 00:05:14.080 align:middle line:84%
under the door so there
would be no light.

00:05:14.080 --> 00:05:14.880 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Huh.

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:17.110 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I then realized I
didn't know any dead people.

00:05:17.110 --> 00:05:19.380 align:middle line:84%
So I was, like, well, Marilyn
Monroe and John Kennedy--

00:05:19.380 --> 00:05:20.180 align:middle line:90%
they're dead.

00:05:20.180 --> 00:05:22.710 align:middle line:84%
It's the late 60s,
so immediately, I

00:05:22.710 --> 00:05:24.030 align:middle line:90%
came up with my first chant.

00:05:24.030 --> 00:05:26.860 align:middle line:84%
It was just kind of inside
of me, and what to say.

00:05:26.860 --> 00:05:29.560 align:middle line:84%
And my little windowless,
lifeless hallway

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:33.580 align:middle line:84%
filled with orbs and lights
and things flying around.

00:05:33.580 --> 00:05:36.550 align:middle line:84%
And me and my
girlfriend, Sheri Jones,

00:05:36.550 --> 00:05:38.230 align:middle line:90%
ran out of the room screaming.

00:05:38.230 --> 00:05:40.810 align:middle line:84%
But inside, I'm like,
yes, this is real.

00:05:40.810 --> 00:05:43.900 align:middle line:84%
So I spent my entire life
figuring out what it was

00:05:43.900 --> 00:05:45.407 align:middle line:90%
and developing and embracing it.

00:05:45.407 --> 00:05:47.740 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, let's take a
look at more of what you do.

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:48.700 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: OK.

00:05:48.700 --> 00:05:50.050 align:middle line:10%
My name is Patty Negri.

00:05:50.050 --> 00:05:52.510 align:middle line:10%
Thank you for coming
to my website.

00:05:52.510 --> 00:05:54.880 align:middle line:84%
Here, you're going to find
a little bit about what I do

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:56.240 align:middle line:90%
and who I am.

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:58.150 align:middle line:84%
But I'll give you a
real quick start--

00:05:58.150 --> 00:05:59.830 align:middle line:90%
I'm a psychic medium.

00:05:59.830 --> 00:06:03.640 align:middle line:10%
I was actually voted top psychic
in the United States this year,

00:06:03.640 --> 00:06:06.670 align:middle line:10%
and top medium and tarot
reader in the world.

00:06:06.670 --> 00:06:08.440 align:middle line:10%
I actually had the
honor of gracing,

00:06:08.440 --> 00:06:10.180 align:middle line:10%
like, five different
magazine covers

00:06:10.180 --> 00:06:12.950 align:middle line:10%
and being in 20 different books
over the last year, or two.

00:06:12.950 --> 00:06:17.342 align:middle line:10%
So I'm very honored and
humbled and grateful.

00:06:17.342 --> 00:06:19.300 align:middle line:84%
I knew when I was two or
three years old that I

00:06:19.300 --> 00:06:20.750 align:middle line:90%
was a little bit different.

00:06:20.750 --> 00:06:22.960 align:middle line:84%
I knew that the so-called
"imaginary friends"

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:25.390 align:middle line:84%
that kids have in the
closet and under the bed

00:06:25.390 --> 00:06:26.865 align:middle line:90%
weren't imaginary at all.

00:06:26.865 --> 00:06:28.240 align:middle line:84%
They were real
beings and I could

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:30.150 align:middle line:90%
talk to and communicate with.

00:06:30.150 --> 00:06:32.530 align:middle line:90%
I worked elementally in my work.

00:06:32.530 --> 00:06:34.090 align:middle line:84%
I do regular
readings with people.

00:06:34.090 --> 00:06:35.200 align:middle line:90%
I do tarot.

00:06:35.200 --> 00:06:37.900 align:middle line:84%
But my specialty is
really moving energy.

00:06:37.900 --> 00:06:39.640 align:middle line:90%
I see through the veil.

00:06:39.640 --> 00:06:43.000 align:middle line:84%
I see the energy and where
it needs shifting and moving.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:45.280 align:middle line:84%
So whether we're doing
a journey session,

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:48.640 align:middle line:84%
we're doing a spell-working,
we're doing a ritual together,

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:51.220 align:middle line:84%
or just a straight tarot
reading or a divination

00:06:51.220 --> 00:06:54.190 align:middle line:84%
of another form, what you're
going to come away with

00:06:54.190 --> 00:06:57.730 align:middle line:84%
is a clearer path,
a clearer picture

00:06:57.730 --> 00:06:59.650 align:middle line:90%
of what to do with your life.

00:06:59.650 --> 00:07:00.790 align:middle line:90%
I'm also a witch.

00:07:00.790 --> 00:07:02.650 align:middle line:84%
I'm a good witch,
or a white witch.

00:07:02.650 --> 00:07:04.370 align:middle line:90%
I don't worship the devil.

00:07:04.370 --> 00:07:06.190 align:middle line:90%
I don't turn people into frogs.

00:07:06.190 --> 00:07:07.480 align:middle line:90%
But I do believe in magic.

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:09.520 align:middle line:84%
I do believe in
magic is everywhere--

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:14.050 align:middle line:84%
in the trees, in the stars,
in stones, and herbs and oils

00:07:14.050 --> 00:07:14.910 align:middle line:90%
and sounds.

00:07:14.910 --> 00:07:15.993 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You're a psychic.

00:07:15.993 --> 00:07:16.900 align:middle line:90%
You're a medium.

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:18.220 align:middle line:90%
How did the witchcraft happen?

00:07:18.220 --> 00:07:19.947 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: The
witchcraft, again, I

00:07:19.947 --> 00:07:21.280 align:middle line:90%
think it's sort of in the blood.

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.950 align:middle line:84%
It's a knowledge, whether it
comes from the great unknown,

00:07:23.950 --> 00:07:25.030 align:middle line:90%
Akashic records.

00:07:25.030 --> 00:07:28.780 align:middle line:84%
But I would find myself in
my little suburban backyard

00:07:28.780 --> 00:07:30.790 align:middle line:84%
picking Rosemary and
knowing what to do with it.

00:07:30.790 --> 00:07:33.330 align:middle line:84%
Putting some in my mom's
wallet to bring her more money.

00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:33.510 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:07:33.510 --> 00:07:34.815 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: And it's just--

00:07:34.815 --> 00:07:36.190 align:middle line:84%
and then, of
course, I studied it

00:07:36.190 --> 00:07:38.273 align:middle line:84%
because I'm a believer in
learn what you're doing,

00:07:38.273 --> 00:07:40.660 align:middle line:90%
as well, versus all natural.

00:07:40.660 --> 00:07:44.950 align:middle line:84%
And once I started studying
belief systems, cosmologies,

00:07:44.950 --> 00:07:48.280 align:middle line:84%
religions, I decided this
was a nice, romantic one.

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:49.960 align:middle line:84%
I think they all have
beautiful truths.

00:07:49.960 --> 00:07:51.970 align:middle line:84%
They're just kind of,
to me, like a template

00:07:51.970 --> 00:07:54.460 align:middle line:84%
you step on top what
path you want to use,

00:07:54.460 --> 00:07:57.220 align:middle line:84%
what cosmology,
what wording system.

00:07:57.220 --> 00:07:58.570 align:middle line:90%
And the pagan one is pretty fun.

00:07:58.570 --> 00:08:00.933 align:middle line:84%
You get to wear cloaks
and dance around bonfires.

00:08:00.933 --> 00:08:02.350 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Patti,
what has Hollywood

00:08:02.350 --> 00:08:04.480 align:middle line:90%
done to the image of witches?

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:07.550 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Well, it's
getting a lot better.

00:08:07.550 --> 00:08:10.340 align:middle line:84%
But it's always been
negative-- the big, ugly, old--

00:08:10.340 --> 00:08:12.340 align:middle line:84%
I don't have a wart on
my nose and they're not--

00:08:12.340 --> 00:08:12.570 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Can I look?

00:08:12.570 --> 00:08:13.780 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: --eating babies.

00:08:13.780 --> 00:08:14.800 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Nope, no wart.

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:15.300 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: No, I don't.

00:08:15.300 --> 00:08:16.195 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: No wart.

00:08:16.195 --> 00:08:19.810 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: So over the years,
it's scary because, again,

00:08:19.810 --> 00:08:24.430 align:middle line:84%
whether Hollywood has done
it or religion has done it,

00:08:24.430 --> 00:08:25.840 align:middle line:90%
it's been bad.

00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:26.950 align:middle line:90%
But it's getting better.

00:08:26.950 --> 00:08:29.890 align:middle line:84%
I mean, even some silly shows
like "Charmed," that came back.

00:08:29.890 --> 00:08:30.690 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:08:30.690 --> 00:08:32.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: They at least
made them good witches

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.130 align:middle line:90%
and they did good things.

00:08:33.130 --> 00:08:33.700 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, "Bewitched"
was a fun show.

00:08:33.700 --> 00:08:36.250 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: "Bewitched"
was a fun show.

00:08:36.250 --> 00:08:38.210 align:middle line:84%
I'm still working
on that nose wiggle.

00:08:38.210 --> 00:08:38.650 align:middle line:90%
I haven't got that yet.

00:08:38.650 --> 00:08:40.740 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Elizabeth
Montgomery was a great witch.

00:08:40.740 --> 00:08:42.282 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, she
was a great witch.

00:08:42.282 --> 00:08:44.780 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now her mother,
played by Agnes Moorehead, eh,

00:08:44.780 --> 00:08:46.450 align:middle line:90%
was a little evil, wasn't it?

00:08:46.450 --> 00:08:50.035 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Well, she was
mother-in-law-y, mother-y.

00:08:50.035 --> 00:08:51.660 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if evil
is the right word.

00:08:51.660 --> 00:08:52.425 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Now to be psychic--

00:08:52.425 --> 00:08:52.990 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yeah.

00:08:52.990 --> 00:08:54.573 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: --what does
that mean to you?

00:08:54.573 --> 00:08:58.330 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: To me, that means,
again, just having a knowledge,

00:08:58.330 --> 00:09:02.650 align:middle line:84%
or I see it, again, as energy,
kind of knowing a path that

00:09:02.650 --> 00:09:03.910 align:middle line:90%
looks like a path is coming.

00:09:03.910 --> 00:09:05.440 align:middle line:84%
Kind of knowing
that the phone is

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:07.638 align:middle line:84%
going to ring, kind of
knowing that somebody

00:09:07.638 --> 00:09:09.430 align:middle line:84%
is going to have certain
kind of struggles,

00:09:09.430 --> 00:09:12.380 align:middle line:84%
or could have struggles-- that's
where my, again, witchness

00:09:12.380 --> 00:09:13.180 align:middle line:90%
wants it going.

00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:15.580 align:middle line:84%
OK, you could have a
tough financial year.

00:09:15.580 --> 00:09:17.980 align:middle line:84%
Let's do something to change
your perception on money.

00:09:17.980 --> 00:09:19.510 align:middle line:84%
Let's do something
to change that,

00:09:19.510 --> 00:09:22.000 align:middle line:84%
whether it's a
spell-working or what.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.920 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Is a spell
something from within,

00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:25.765 align:middle line:90%
or is it something from outside?

00:09:25.765 --> 00:09:26.820 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yes, both.

00:09:26.820 --> 00:09:27.620 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It is?

00:09:27.620 --> 00:09:32.680 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I'm a big believer in
that mind-body-spirit thing.

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:35.980 align:middle line:84%
200,000 books are written about
mind-body-spirit, self-help,

00:09:35.980 --> 00:09:38.540 align:middle line:90%
spirituality, psychology.

00:09:38.540 --> 00:09:40.700 align:middle line:84%
We will never surpass
our thought pattern.

00:09:40.700 --> 00:09:43.780 align:middle line:84%
so you have to believe that, so
that's part of spell-working.

00:09:43.780 --> 00:09:46.990 align:middle line:84%
The body-mind, the body
part taking action.

00:09:46.990 --> 00:09:49.588 align:middle line:84%
But the spirit, that's
the part most people miss.

00:09:49.588 --> 00:09:51.130 align:middle line:84%
One out of three is
wishful thinking.

00:09:51.130 --> 00:09:53.230 align:middle line:90%
Two out of three is hit or miss.

00:09:53.230 --> 00:09:54.730 align:middle line:84%
Three out of three
is a home-run.

00:09:54.730 --> 00:09:58.060 align:middle line:84%
The spell-working could
be the magic behind it.

00:09:58.060 --> 00:09:59.170 align:middle line:90%
It's the battery power.

00:09:59.170 --> 00:10:01.600 align:middle line:84%
So it could also be done
through prayer-- go to church,

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:04.550 align:middle line:84%
go to temple,
affirmations, new age.

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:07.430 align:middle line:84%
It could be done through
positive thinking or vision

00:10:07.430 --> 00:10:08.230 align:middle line:90%
boards.

00:10:08.230 --> 00:10:10.870 align:middle line:84%
But I kind of like
burning herbs and oils,

00:10:10.870 --> 00:10:13.330 align:middle line:90%
and candles and chants.

00:10:13.330 --> 00:10:18.820 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Can you use the wrong
spell for the right thing?

00:10:18.820 --> 00:10:19.990 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I don't know.

00:10:19.990 --> 00:10:21.867 align:middle line:90%
Right and wrong is--

00:10:21.867 --> 00:10:22.700 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Subjective.

00:10:22.700 --> 00:10:23.980 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: It's very subjective.

00:10:23.980 --> 00:10:28.350 align:middle line:84%
I don't believe that there's
an exact way to do anything.

00:10:28.350 --> 00:10:31.990 align:middle line:84%
I do believe your intent
is what's right or wrong.

00:10:31.990 --> 00:10:34.382 align:middle line:84%
I don't know about
what a wrong spell is.

00:10:34.382 --> 00:10:36.090 align:middle line:84%
Like you're supposed
to use a red candle,

00:10:36.090 --> 00:10:37.200 align:middle line:90%
but all you have is purple?

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:38.010 align:middle line:90%
Use the purple.

00:10:38.010 --> 00:10:39.830 align:middle line:84%
Or you feel purple
is the right candle--

00:10:39.830 --> 00:10:40.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Right,
something's not going

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:41.570 align:middle line:90%
to happen and backfire on you.

00:10:41.570 --> 00:10:44.400 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: But the about
the "bad" spell-working

00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:46.860 align:middle line:84%
is doing anything that
manipulates anybody else.

00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:49.290 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Your book, "Magick
For the Modern World--"

00:10:49.290 --> 00:10:50.190 align:middle line:90%
tell me about that.

00:10:50.190 --> 00:10:52.830 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: OK, that was my--
it's a really simple book.

00:10:52.830 --> 00:10:55.350 align:middle line:84%
I honestly spent more
time unwriting it,

00:10:55.350 --> 00:10:58.690 align:middle line:84%
because when I started,
what, 30-some years ago,

00:10:58.690 --> 00:10:59.490 align:middle line:90%
I get these--

00:10:59.490 --> 00:11:01.365 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What, were you
two when you started?

00:11:01.365 --> 00:11:02.760 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yes, yes, two--

00:11:02.760 --> 00:11:04.080 align:middle line:90%
I wish.

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:05.395 align:middle line:90%
Nah, I love it.

00:11:05.395 --> 00:11:07.020 align:middle line:84%
I would get these
big, beautiful books,

00:11:07.020 --> 00:11:08.145 align:middle line:90%
but they'd be overwhelming.

00:11:08.145 --> 00:11:10.740 align:middle line:84%
And then I'd get a simple
little book that was really easy

00:11:10.740 --> 00:11:12.600 align:middle line:84%
and I could relate
to, and that's

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:13.950 align:middle line:90%
what I wanted this to be.

00:11:13.950 --> 00:11:16.360 align:middle line:84%
It's not made for
psychics or mediums.

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:18.090 align:middle line:90%
It can be any belief system.

00:11:18.090 --> 00:11:21.120 align:middle line:84%
But it's about, again,
that empowering people.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:23.610 align:middle line:84%
It's how to relax
when you can't relax.

00:11:23.610 --> 00:11:26.070 align:middle line:84%
If your head gets chatty,
how to relax that.

00:11:26.070 --> 00:11:28.620 align:middle line:84%
Yes, it's great to
meditate for an hour.

00:11:28.620 --> 00:11:30.180 align:middle line:84%
But we usually
don't have an hour.

00:11:30.180 --> 00:11:32.470 align:middle line:84%
We have 30 seconds
to pull it together.

00:11:32.470 --> 00:11:35.200 align:middle line:84%
So I take my "magical"
techniques, like hug

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:37.800 align:middle line:84%
a tree to relax, or run
your hands under water.

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:38.950 align:middle line:90%
That's your water element.

00:11:38.950 --> 00:11:39.750 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Huh.

00:11:39.750 --> 00:11:43.035 align:middle line:84%
You end the word magic
in your book with a K--

00:11:43.035 --> 00:11:45.823 align:middle line:90%
M-A-G-I-C-K-- how come?

00:11:45.823 --> 00:11:47.490 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: To me, that
is what delineates,

00:11:47.490 --> 00:11:49.500 align:middle line:84%
and that's kind of
how the world sees it.

00:11:49.500 --> 00:11:50.917 align:middle line:84%
The difference of
magic with the C

00:11:50.917 --> 00:11:52.833 align:middle line:84%
means you could pull a
rabbit out of your hat,

00:11:52.833 --> 00:11:53.920 align:middle line:90%
or do card tricks.

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:56.880 align:middle line:84%
Magick with a K means you're
doing the kind of magic that

00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:58.120 align:middle line:90%
isn't an illusion.

00:11:58.120 --> 00:11:59.370 align:middle line:90%
It's really shifting.

00:11:59.370 --> 00:12:01.440 align:middle line:84%
To me, that's what
magic, or spell-working,

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:03.870 align:middle line:84%
or anything-- something
that causes a shift

00:12:03.870 --> 00:12:06.240 align:middle line:90%
in the natural trajectory.

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:09.480 align:middle line:84%
In life, nature,
everything kind of

00:12:09.480 --> 00:12:12.660 align:middle line:84%
goes in the easiest pattern
to me-- almost flows

00:12:12.660 --> 00:12:13.710 align:middle line:90%
downhill like gravity.

00:12:13.710 --> 00:12:14.510 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Mm-hmm.

00:12:14.510 --> 00:12:16.500 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Our life, if
we don't put this to it,

00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:18.450 align:middle line:84%
just is going to
take the easy path.

00:12:18.450 --> 00:12:20.280 align:middle line:84%
Magic is going
[EXHALES QUICKLY]..

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:23.220 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to shift that,
whether it's my perception,

00:12:23.220 --> 00:12:25.710 align:middle line:84%
or myself around
the world within me.

00:12:25.710 --> 00:12:27.900 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Patti, are you
almost like a psychologist

00:12:27.900 --> 00:12:29.080 align:middle line:90%
when you're dealing with us?

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:30.830 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I am so much
like a psychologist.

00:12:30.830 --> 00:12:33.060 align:middle line:84%
My atheist grandfather
would be proud

00:12:33.060 --> 00:12:34.750 align:middle line:90%
because he was a psychologist.

00:12:34.750 --> 00:12:36.630 align:middle line:84%
He worked with this
whole Hollywood set.

00:12:36.630 --> 00:12:38.070 align:middle line:90%
And I find myself there.

00:12:38.070 --> 00:12:41.108 align:middle line:84%
It's-- yeah, I'm not a
trained psychologist.

00:12:41.108 --> 00:12:42.150 align:middle line:90%
But I'm pretty damn good.

00:12:42.150 --> 00:12:44.270 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You said your
atheist grandfather--

00:12:44.270 --> 00:12:45.070 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yes.

00:12:45.070 --> 00:12:46.290 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: --atheist.

00:12:46.290 --> 00:12:47.820 align:middle line:84%
What do you think
he's doing now?

00:12:47.820 --> 00:12:52.220 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I think-- I've
actually spoken to him and he--

00:12:52.220 --> 00:12:54.000 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Did he say
that he was wrong?

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:57.630 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: He wouldn't use the
word 'wrong,' but he sees

00:12:57.630 --> 00:12:59.040 align:middle line:90%
an expanded view.

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:01.410 align:middle line:84%
My thing-- and again,
talking to the other side,

00:13:01.410 --> 00:13:04.920 align:middle line:84%
people don't get
angelic, or get wise.

00:13:04.920 --> 00:13:08.370 align:middle line:84%
But they almost always get a
slightly higher perspective,

00:13:08.370 --> 00:13:11.430 align:middle line:84%
a bigger view, whether it's
literally a higher perspective.

00:13:11.430 --> 00:13:14.680 align:middle line:84%
So a lot of the petty things,
the little things get resolved.

00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:15.990 align:middle line:90%
There's still them, but--

00:13:15.990 --> 00:13:18.390 align:middle line:90%
I read his books now.

00:13:18.390 --> 00:13:19.980 align:middle line:90%
He wrote lots of books.

00:13:19.980 --> 00:13:22.895 align:middle line:84%
And where they were just
undoing belief systems,

00:13:22.895 --> 00:13:24.270 align:middle line:84%
and he knew more
about religion--

00:13:24.270 --> 00:13:24.900 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: He was a skeptic.

00:13:24.900 --> 00:13:26.250 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: He was a skeptic.

00:13:26.250 --> 00:13:29.220 align:middle line:84%
But I read his books now and
it's almost the same belief

00:13:29.220 --> 00:13:30.870 align:middle line:90%
system, just different words.

00:13:30.870 --> 00:13:33.330 align:middle line:84%
He would use scientific
and academic words,

00:13:33.330 --> 00:13:36.720 align:middle line:84%
while somebody else will
use Judeo-Christian words,

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:38.760 align:middle line:84%
or somebody else
will use pagan words.

00:13:38.760 --> 00:13:40.950 align:middle line:84%
But that basic
truth is the same.

00:13:40.950 --> 00:13:42.880 align:middle line:84%
So I read his books and
it's like, that's not

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:43.680 align:middle line:90%
all that different.

00:13:43.680 --> 00:13:46.260 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Taking religion out
of the equation for a moment,

00:13:46.260 --> 00:13:50.370 align:middle line:84%
the reason why I think there's
another side, the afterlife,

00:13:50.370 --> 00:13:53.570 align:middle line:84%
is because we can't explain why
we're here in the first place.

00:13:53.570 --> 00:13:54.370 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yeah.

00:13:54.370 --> 00:13:56.610 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: This
unbelievable wonderment

00:13:56.610 --> 00:14:00.540 align:middle line:84%
of what life is just
simply carries on.

00:14:00.540 --> 00:14:05.580 align:middle line:84%
And to me, it's not we're
alive, we die, that's it.

00:14:05.580 --> 00:14:08.230 align:middle line:84%
People can't explain how we
got here in the first place.

00:14:08.230 --> 00:14:10.720 align:middle line:84%
Again, taking religion
out of the equation--

00:14:10.720 --> 00:14:13.600 align:middle line:84%
that's the easy way of
saying, oh, god made us.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:17.190 align:middle line:84%
But with that aside,
how do we get here?

00:14:17.190 --> 00:14:20.250 align:middle line:84%
And if that's the case, and
if you can't answer that,

00:14:20.250 --> 00:14:23.050 align:middle line:84%
you can't negate the
possibility of an afterlife.

00:14:23.050 --> 00:14:23.850 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yeah.

00:14:23.850 --> 00:14:25.710 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And I've
always thought that.

00:14:25.710 --> 00:14:28.350 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, and I love
the what-we-don't-know part.

00:14:28.350 --> 00:14:30.960 align:middle line:84%
Some people want to know
things and they have firm--

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:33.840 align:middle line:84%
and I think that's why most
religion was even created,

00:14:33.840 --> 00:14:37.080 align:middle line:84%
to give us, well, this is this,
and so it explains something.

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.550 align:middle line:90%
I love the unknown.

00:14:38.550 --> 00:14:42.780 align:middle line:84%
I love what I don't know,
and we don't know a lot.

00:14:42.780 --> 00:14:44.310 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What is magic to you?

00:14:44.310 --> 00:14:47.220 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Magic to me is,
again, causing a shift,

00:14:47.220 --> 00:14:50.100 align:middle line:90%
causing a change, and taking--

00:14:50.100 --> 00:14:53.190 align:middle line:84%
basically, taking power--
taking power over your own life,

00:14:53.190 --> 00:14:55.380 align:middle line:84%
taking power over
your situation,

00:14:55.380 --> 00:15:00.030 align:middle line:84%
taking power over
love, finances, health.

00:15:00.030 --> 00:15:02.490 align:middle line:84%
I would be extraordinarily
sick or dead if I

00:15:02.490 --> 00:15:03.510 align:middle line:90%
didn't believe in magic.

00:15:03.510 --> 00:15:04.210 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Really?

00:15:04.210 --> 00:15:04.660 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yeah.

00:15:04.660 --> 00:15:05.460 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Dead?

00:15:05.460 --> 00:15:06.900 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Dead, I would be dead.

00:15:06.900 --> 00:15:07.380 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's pretty strong.

00:15:07.380 --> 00:15:08.310 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I would be dead.

00:15:08.310 --> 00:15:09.110 align:middle line:90%
I would be dead.

00:15:09.110 --> 00:15:11.270 align:middle line:90%
I was-- probably.

00:15:11.270 --> 00:15:14.670 align:middle line:84%
The dying-- part of
my little journey

00:15:14.670 --> 00:15:16.860 align:middle line:84%
is I was diagnosed
when I was a teenager

00:15:16.860 --> 00:15:18.040 align:middle line:90%
with diethylstilbestrol.

00:15:18.040 --> 00:15:18.840 align:middle line:90%
It's a--

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:20.040 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What the heck is that?

00:15:20.040 --> 00:15:22.373 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: It's a drug they
gave pregnant women in the 50s

00:15:22.373 --> 00:15:26.483 align:middle line:84%
and 60s under the false belief
that it prevented miscarriage.

00:15:26.483 --> 00:15:28.400 align:middle line:84%
They didn't know it was
a horrible carcinogen.

00:15:28.400 --> 00:15:30.240 align:middle line:84%
When we hit puberty,
we started dying.

00:15:30.240 --> 00:15:31.040 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, geez.

00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:34.790 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I basically went
menopausal at puberty instead.

