I got on that TV
show "Wipe Out."

00:16:16.052 --> 00:16:17.510 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You've
done a lot of that.

00:16:17.510 --> 00:16:19.177 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I've done a
lot of weird things

00:16:19.177 --> 00:16:22.118 align:middle line:84%
to just prove how
amazing humans are.

00:16:22.118 --> 00:16:23.660 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, you
remember that drug

00:16:23.660 --> 00:16:25.970 align:middle line:84%
they gave women who were
pregnant-- thalidomide?

00:16:25.970 --> 00:16:27.720 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Thalidomide--
the flipper babies.

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:29.095 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And the
kids were born--

00:16:29.095 --> 00:16:30.560 align:middle line:84%
