flipper hands.

00:16:30.560 --> 00:16:32.768 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: And ours was just
as bad or worse than that,

00:16:32.768 --> 00:16:34.280 align:middle line:84%
but the people
don't know about it

00:16:34.280 --> 00:16:36.920 align:middle line:84%
