But it was considered the
biggest American tragedy ever.

00:16:41.750 --> 00:16:42.668 align:middle line:90%
10 million people--

00:16:42.668 --> 00:16:43.710 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It was horrible.

00:16:43.710 --> 00:16:45.980 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: --effected
by it worldwide.

00:16:45.980 --> 00:16:49.100 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now when you talked
about coming out of the closet,

00:16:49.100 --> 00:16:50.270 align:middle line:90%
