00:16:50.270 --> 00:16:52.128 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: [LAUGHS] I
use my broom every day.

00:16:52.128 --> 00:16:53.670 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Witches do
that, don't they?

00:16:53.670 --> 00:16:55.730 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yes, they do.

00:16:55.730 --> 00:16:57.070 align:middle line:90%
The broom is actually the best.

00:16:57.070 --> 00:16:58.850 align:middle line:84%
And the witch's
broom, it's actually

00:16:58.850 --> 00:17:00.920 align:middle line:84%
