between the world.

00:17:00.920 --> 00:17:03.563 align:middle line:84%
Not so much straddling
it and flying--

00:17:03.563 --> 00:17:05.480 align:middle line:84%
I haven't gotten off the
ground with that yet.

00:17:05.480 --> 00:17:08.640 align:middle line:84%
