and you pay your bills.

00:17:15.020 --> 00:17:17.930 align:middle line:84%
That side is a wonderment
where anything can happen.

00:17:17.930 --> 00:17:20.870 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Patti, when people come
to you, what do they ask for,

00:17:20.870 --> 00:17:21.670 align:middle line:90%
primarily?

00:17:21.670 --> 00:17:22.079 align:middle line:90%
What do they want?

00:17:22.079 --> 00:17:23.599 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: OK, when
people come to me,

00:17:23.599 --> 00:17:26.660 align:middle line:84%
it's usually because something
in their life isn't going well.

00:17:26.660 --> 00:17:29.090 align:middle line:84%
And like with anybody
who works in this field,

00:17:29.090 --> 00:17:30.570 align:middle line:90%
love is number one.

00:17:30.570 --> 00:17:32.720 align:middle line:84%
[CHUCKLES] It's love
isn't working right,

00:17:32.720 --> 00:17:34.530 align:middle line:84%
or they can't find the
love of their life,

00:17:34.530 --> 00:17:36.590 align:middle line:90%
or whatever that is.

00:17:36.590 --> 00:17:39.330 align:middle line:84%
Love first, and then money and
career second, and then health,

00:17:39.330 --> 00:17:40.130 align:middle line:90%
third.

00:17:40.130 --> 00:17:41.755 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So when
people read your book,

00:17:41.755 --> 00:17:43.550 align:middle line:84%
"Magick For the
Modern World," what's

00:17:43.550 --> 00:17:45.575 align:middle line:84%
the big thing you
want them to grasp?

00:17:45.575 --> 00:17:47.450 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: The big thing
I want them to grasp

00:17:47.450 --> 00:17:50.960 align:middle line:84%
is that it's really easy
to change your life.

00:17:50.960 --> 00:17:52.280 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't take money.

00:17:52.280 --> 00:17:53.760 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't take a lot of time.

00:17:53.760 --> 00:17:56.990 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't take a
thought-provoking anything.

00:17:56.990 --> 00:17:59.143 align:middle line:84%
Literally, if you've got
something you feel like

00:17:59.143 --> 00:18:00.560 align:middle line:84%
it's a curse,
because most aren't.

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:01.520 align:middle line:90%
Well, grab a lemon.

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:03.230 align:middle line:90%
Grab some salt. Do this thing.

00:18:03.230 --> 00:18:04.130 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:18:04.130 --> 00:18:05.210 align:middle line:90%
It goes away.

00:18:05.210 --> 00:18:07.510 align:middle line:84%
Again, I'm combining
that belief system,

00:18:07.510 --> 00:18:09.500 align:middle line:84%
that a body of
action and the magic

00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:11.300 align:middle line:84%
that's in the
lemon and the salt.

00:18:11.300 --> 00:18:14.810 align:middle line:84%
But again, I think I'm mostly
proud of those elemental

00:18:14.810 --> 00:18:17.090 align:middle line:90%
exercises I do that can--

00:18:17.090 --> 00:18:19.310 align:middle line:84%
I say 30 seconds to
cure almost anything.

00:18:19.310 --> 00:18:21.650 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How do
you know it works?

00:18:21.650 --> 00:18:22.820 align:middle line:90%
You see results, I assume?

00:18:22.820 --> 00:18:23.600 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I see results.

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:24.400 align:middle line:90%
I see results.

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:27.177 align:middle line:84%
I've seen people,
again, find that love

00:18:27.177 --> 00:18:29.510 align:middle line:84%
of their life, where they've
married the wrong person 10

00:18:29.510 --> 00:18:30.310 align:middle line:90%
times.

00:18:30.310 --> 00:18:32.960 align:middle line:84%
I've seen people change
their financial situations.

00:18:32.960 --> 00:18:35.090 align:middle line:84%
More than anything,
their health situations,

00:18:35.090 --> 00:18:36.560 align:middle line:84%
because this is the most
important thing we have--

00:18:36.560 --> 00:18:37.850 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Because of
you, or because of them?

00:18:37.850 --> 00:18:39.200 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Not because of me.

00:18:39.200 --> 00:18:40.130 align:middle line:90%
I don't do anything.

00:18:40.130 --> 00:18:41.390 align:middle line:84%
I just give them
some suggestions.

00:18:41.390 --> 00:18:42.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, you
cast the spells.

00:18:42.320 --> 00:18:44.225 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I cast-- no,
we do it together.

00:18:44.225 --> 00:18:45.025 align:middle line:90%
We do it together.

00:18:45.025 --> 00:18:47.700 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Like the money spell,
the love spell, the health

00:18:47.700 --> 00:18:48.860 align:middle line:90%
spell-- you do it together?

00:18:48.860 --> 00:18:50.330 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: We do it together.

00:18:50.330 --> 00:18:52.190 align:middle line:90%
I'm not going to go off--

00:18:52.190 --> 00:18:55.400 align:middle line:84%
because again, for every
one legitimate one of me

