>>NOORY: I like that.

00:19:18.170 --> 00:19:18.510 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Thank you.

00:19:18.510 --> 00:19:20.510 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And you talked
about a spell for money.

00:19:20.510 --> 00:19:22.490 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Yes, let's look.

00:19:22.490 --> 00:19:24.650 align:middle line:84%
I think we're ready to
cast our first spell--

00:19:24.650 --> 00:19:27.010 align:middle line:90%
my money spell.

00:19:27.010 --> 00:19:30.350 align:middle line:84%
First, what you'll need,
of course, is money.

00:19:30.350 --> 00:19:34.550 align:middle line:84%
Just $1 bill, but I should warn
you, we are going to burn it.

00:19:34.550 --> 00:19:37.500 align:middle line:84%
So first, to create your
space, light your candle

00:19:37.500 --> 00:19:38.300 align:middle line:90%
and the incense.

00:19:38.300 --> 00:19:41.360 align:middle line:90%


00:19:41.360 --> 00:19:43.490 align:middle line:84%
As you light your
candle and your incense,

00:19:43.490 --> 00:19:46.950 align:middle line:84%
I want you thinking about
all the wonderful things

00:19:46.950 --> 00:19:50.100 align:middle line:84%
that some extra money can
bring in to your life--

00:19:50.100 --> 00:19:55.740 align:middle line:84%
ease, grace, happiness,
new shoes, paid off debts.

00:19:55.740 --> 00:19:59.020 align:middle line:84%
And as you're thinking about it,
I want you to smell that money.

00:19:59.020 --> 00:20:00.230 align:middle line:90%
I want you to taste it.

00:20:00.230 --> 00:20:03.480 align:middle line:84%
I want you to feel it in
every cell of your bone.

00:20:03.480 --> 00:20:06.620 align:middle line:84%
And when you really got a good
visual, once you could really

00:20:06.620 --> 00:20:09.800 align:middle line:84%
feel it, I want you to start
writing it on the dollar

00:20:09.800 --> 00:20:11.630 align:middle line:90%
bill with passion.

00:20:11.630 --> 00:20:13.550 align:middle line:84%
This is that
important part again.

00:20:13.550 --> 00:20:15.290 align:middle line:84%
And then to add
the air element, I

00:20:15.290 --> 00:20:18.380 align:middle line:84%
want you to waft it through
the incense three times--

00:20:18.380 --> 00:20:20.870 align:middle line:90%
one, two, three.

00:20:20.870 --> 00:20:24.350 align:middle line:84%
Then I want you to lay it
over the candle three times

00:20:24.350 --> 00:20:26.540 align:middle line:90%
as you watch the flame.

00:20:26.540 --> 00:20:30.752 align:middle line:84%
And on that third time,
I want you to light it.

00:20:30.752 --> 00:20:32.680 align:middle line:90%
[VOCALIZING]

00:20:32.680 --> 00:20:37.500 align:middle line:90%


00:20:37.500 --> 00:20:38.950 align:middle line:90%
[SCREAMS]

00:20:38.950 --> 00:20:41.470 align:middle line:84%
By the power of
three times three,

00:20:41.470 --> 00:20:44.330 align:middle line:90%
this spell bound round shall be.

00:20:44.330 --> 00:20:45.130 align:middle line:90%
You could say that.

00:20:45.130 --> 00:20:46.380 align:middle line:90%
Or you could say, amen.

00:20:46.380 --> 00:20:47.660 align:middle line:90%
Or you could say, ah-ho--

00:20:47.660 --> 00:20:50.530 align:middle line:84%
just something to go, this
is complete and this is done.

00:20:50.530 --> 00:20:52.540 align:middle line:84%
Now remember the
one real rule is

00:20:52.540 --> 00:20:54.820 align:middle line:84%
don't do spell-working
on anybody else,

00:20:54.820 --> 00:20:57.790 align:middle line:84%
and always stay in integrity
and work in the light,

00:20:57.790 --> 00:20:58.830 align:middle line:90%
and all will be well.

00:20:58.830 --> 00:21:01.420 align:middle line:84%
So post a comment
below when your spell

00:21:01.420 --> 00:21:03.130 align:middle line:90%
starts working because it will.

00:21:03.130 --> 00:21:04.660 align:middle line:90%
Sometimes it's really fast.

00:21:04.660 --> 00:21:06.340 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes it takes
a little while.

00:21:06.340 --> 00:21:09.280 align:middle line:84%
But believe me, it has
brought amazing abundance

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:11.065 align:middle line:84%
to tons of people
over the years.

00:21:11.065 --> 00:21:13.060 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Whoever that
person was is out $1.

00:21:13.060 --> 00:21:14.140 align:middle line:90%
Or was it yours?

00:21:14.140 --> 00:21:16.820 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: [LAUGHS]
That was my dollar.

00:21:16.820 --> 00:21:20.080 align:middle line:10%
But if somebody-- it's so
funny because we have this--

00:21:20.080 --> 00:21:21.880 align:middle line:10%
again, our perceptions
about money,

00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:23.710 align:middle line:10%
the sacred thing about money.

00:21:23.710 --> 00:21:25.110 align:middle line:90%
And though I do think it is--

00:21:25.110 --> 00:21:26.620 align:middle line:84%
probably you're not
supposed to burn money.

00:21:26.620 --> 00:21:28.537 align:middle line:84%
The government doesn't
get mad unless you want

00:21:28.537 --> 00:21:29.737 align:middle line:90%
them to replace it for you.

00:21:29.737 --> 00:21:31.570 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, at least
it wasn't $100 bill.

00:21:31.570 --> 00:21:33.112 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: It wasn't
a $100 bill, but I

00:21:33.112 --> 00:21:36.540 align:middle line:84%
bet you would-- if you put that
importance of that $100 bill,

00:21:36.540 --> 00:21:37.720 align:middle line:90%
it would work even better.

00:21:37.720 --> 00:21:38.660 align:middle line:90%
But you don't need to.

00:21:38.660 --> 00:21:41.380 align:middle line:84%
And if somebody is really
troubled burning a $1 bill,

00:21:41.380 --> 00:21:42.350 align:middle line:90%
use monopoly money.

00:21:42.350 --> 00:21:43.150 align:middle line:90%
Use play money.

00:21:43.150 --> 00:21:44.200 align:middle line:90%
Draw $1.

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.680 align:middle line:84%
I've had people
from Canada going--

00:21:45.680 --> 00:21:46.480 align:middle line:90%
coins.

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:47.650 align:middle line:90%
No, you can't burn a coin.

00:21:47.650 --> 00:21:49.330 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How often
will that come back?

00:21:49.330 --> 00:21:51.310 align:middle line:84%
That dollar will come
back how many times?

00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:54.100 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Oh, I started
doing this in the 80s--

00:21:54.100 --> 00:21:55.720 align:middle line:90%
