and a little baby.

00:23:14.140 --> 00:23:15.730 align:middle line:84%
It was horrible,
just seeing that.

00:23:15.730 --> 00:23:17.680 align:middle line:90%
I gave him $20.

00:23:17.680 --> 00:23:20.140 align:middle line:84%
Went into the post office,
opened up my little post office

00:23:20.140 --> 00:23:22.480 align:middle line:84%
box, and there's an
insurance check in there

00:23:22.480 --> 00:23:26.620 align:middle line:84%
that I have no idea
was coming, for $1,500.

00:23:26.620 --> 00:23:27.580 align:middle line:90%
How does that happen?

00:23:27.580 --> 00:23:29.620 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: That's the
law of the universe.

00:23:29.620 --> 00:23:33.640 align:middle line:84%
What you put-- a cause and
effect, action and reaction.

00:23:33.640 --> 00:23:36.280 align:middle line:84%
What you put out
comes back to you.

00:23:36.280 --> 00:23:40.077 align:middle line:84%
That's why I wouldn't do
curses or dark spells.

00:23:40.077 --> 00:23:41.410 align:middle line:90%
Because if you live in a world--

00:23:41.410 --> 00:23:42.785 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to curse
you-- then you

00:23:42.785 --> 00:23:45.340 align:middle line:84%
live in a worse world
where curses exist.

00:23:45.340 --> 00:23:48.100 align:middle line:84%
If you give and you're
generous with your time,

00:23:48.100 --> 00:23:51.472 align:middle line:84%
with your money, with your love,
that's what comes back to you.

00:23:51.472 --> 00:23:53.680 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What's it like to
communicate with the dead?

00:23:53.680 --> 00:23:55.210 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Oh, it's fabulous.

00:23:55.210 --> 00:23:56.290 align:middle line:90%
Dead people are fun.

00:23:56.290 --> 00:23:57.370 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Some of them.

00:23:57.370 --> 00:23:59.890 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Some of them--
yeah, like humans, there's

00:23:59.890 --> 00:24:03.140 align:middle line:84%
good ones and bad ones,
happy ones and cranky ones.

00:24:03.140 --> 00:24:03.940 align:middle line:90%
But I think--

00:24:03.940 --> 00:24:04.740 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Evil ones.

00:24:04.740 --> 00:24:08.200 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Evil ones-- but like
humans, most dead are good.

00:24:08.200 --> 00:24:09.220 align:middle line:90%
Most humans are good.

00:24:09.220 --> 00:24:10.810 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, there's those
serial killers

00:24:10.810 --> 00:24:12.033 align:middle line:90%
out there and those bad guys.

00:24:12.033 --> 00:24:13.825 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do you
communicate with them, too?

00:24:13.825 --> 00:24:15.130 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I have.

00:24:15.130 --> 00:24:16.150 align:middle line:90%
In real life, I don't.

00:24:16.150 --> 00:24:18.610 align:middle line:84%
Like if someone is coming
to a seance at my house,

00:24:18.610 --> 00:24:22.370 align:middle line:84%
we're only going to allow
in their dead loved ones

00:24:22.370 --> 00:24:23.170 align:middle line:90%
and relatives.

00:24:23.170 --> 00:24:25.280 align:middle line:84%
Talk to grandma, even
working the Ouija Board.

00:24:25.280 --> 00:24:26.530 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Can you control that?

00:24:26.530 --> 00:24:28.155 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I can
completely control that.

00:24:28.155 --> 00:24:29.740 align:middle line:90%
This is our realm of existence.

00:24:29.740 --> 00:24:34.250 align:middle line:84%
I firmly believe that the other
side has to play by our rules.

00:24:34.250 --> 00:24:37.210 align:middle line:84%
Witches, we don't know that,
so we give away our power.

00:24:37.210 --> 00:24:38.250 align:middle line:90%
We give away our power.

00:24:38.250 --> 00:24:40.103 align:middle line:84%
So now I can go into
those dark places,

00:24:40.103 --> 00:24:42.520 align:middle line:84%
like on "Ghost Adventures,"
or the show, where they're not

00:24:42.520 --> 00:24:44.590 align:middle line:84%
going to go talk
to grandma ghosts.

00:24:44.590 --> 00:24:47.830 align:middle line:84%
They're going to talk to
the Black Dahlia killer.

00:24:47.830 --> 00:24:50.800 align:middle line:84%
I still believe that I can
walk away from that completely.

00:24:50.800 --> 00:24:52.120 align:middle line:90%
They have to play by our rules.

00:24:52.120 --> 00:24:54.400 align:middle line:84%
We just give our power
over to them with fear,

00:24:54.400 --> 00:24:56.070 align:middle line:84%
or anger, or just
not knowing better.

00:24:56.070 --> 00:24:57.570 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What have
you found, Patti,

00:24:57.570 --> 00:24:59.920 align:middle line:90%
that the dead want with us?

00:24:59.920 --> 00:25:02.150 align:middle line:84%
Why do they communicate
through you, for example?

00:25:02.150 --> 00:25:02.950 align:middle line:90%
What do they want?

00:25:02.950 --> 00:25:05.830 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I think,
well, sometimes they

00:25:05.830 --> 00:25:07.390 align:middle line:90%
have messages they want to give.

00:25:07.390 --> 00:25:10.370 align:middle line:84%
I think the coolest thing, what
they get out of it-- sometimes

00:25:10.370 --> 00:25:11.170 align:middle line:90%
it is.

00:25:11.170 --> 00:25:14.100 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, grandma's
not stuck in the house.

00:25:14.100 --> 00:25:16.822 align:middle line:84%
Every-- oh, it's such a shame
they're not crossed over.

00:25:16.822 --> 00:25:18.280 align:middle line:84%
They're almost
always crossed over.

00:25:18.280 --> 00:25:19.720 align:middle line:90%
They just like to visit.

00:25:19.720 --> 00:25:22.570 align:middle line:84%
But communicating one
on one, whether it's

00:25:22.570 --> 00:25:25.270 align:middle line:84%
a mediumship or
a seance, I don't

00:25:25.270 --> 00:25:27.600 align:middle line:84%
believe that there's time
and space on the other side.

00:25:27.600 --> 00:25:29.260 align:middle line:84%
So they could be
everywhere, anywhere.

00:25:29.260 --> 00:25:33.280 align:middle line:84%
But when we are communicating
one on one, it's real time,

00:25:33.280 --> 00:25:34.810 align:middle line:90%
and they love that.

00:25:34.810 --> 00:25:37.060 align:middle line:84%
So it's like grandma,
what's your--

00:25:37.060 --> 00:25:39.760 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I've literally gotten
iPhone codes from spirits

00:25:39.760 --> 00:25:40.915 align:middle line:90%
so they can open up their--

00:25:40.915 --> 00:25:41.715 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Really?

00:25:41.715 --> 00:25:43.660 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, practical--
I like practical spirits.

00:25:43.660 --> 00:25:45.410 align:middle line:84%
So it's great to go
smell the butterflies,

00:25:45.410 --> 00:25:46.990 align:middle line:84%
but they need to
open this iPhone.

00:25:46.990 --> 00:25:49.940 align:middle line:84%
So they like it because
it's-- you could say,

00:25:49.940 --> 00:25:50.740 align:middle line:90%
how are you doing?

00:25:50.740 --> 00:25:51.700 align:middle line:90%
Where's the will?

00:25:51.700 --> 00:25:53.420 align:middle line:84%
Real time-- and
so it's a win-win.

00:25:53.420 --> 00:25:54.220 align:middle line:90%
We get--

00:25:54.220 --> 00:25:55.015 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What's under the bed?

00:25:55.015 --> 00:25:56.320 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: What's under the bed?

00:25:56.320 --> 00:25:59.900 align:middle line:84%
We get from them solace,
happiness, information--

00:25:59.900 --> 00:26:00.700 align:middle line:90%
whatever we get.

00:26:00.700 --> 00:26:03.298 align:middle line:84%
But they get real
with time, one on one,

00:26:03.298 --> 00:26:04.840 align:middle line:84%
and I think that's
the one thing they

00:26:04.840 --> 00:26:05.860 align:middle line:90%
don't have on the other side.

00:26:05.860 --> 00:26:07.635 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Pretty remarkable--
you do a lot of seances?

00:26:07.635 --> 00:26:09.020 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I do a lot of seances.

00:26:09.020 --> 00:26:11.720 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Let's take a look
at you conducting a seance,

00:26:11.720 --> 00:26:13.340 align:middle line:90%
so then we'll talk about it.

00:26:13.340 --> 00:26:14.965 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Guardians,
gods, and goddesses

00:26:14.965 --> 00:26:17.290 align:middle line:90%
of the watchtower of the East.

00:26:17.290 --> 00:26:21.130 align:middle line:84%
Calling on gods and goddesses,
and guardians of the South.

00:26:21.130 --> 00:26:24.520 align:middle line:84%
Calling all guardians of
the watchtower of the West.

00:26:24.520 --> 00:26:27.730 align:middle line:84%
Calling all guardians of
the watchtower of the North.

00:26:27.730 --> 00:26:34.850 align:middle line:90%


00:26:34.850 --> 00:26:37.040 align:middle line:84%
So kind of what we
have here is a lot

00:26:37.040 --> 00:26:38.810 align:middle line:84%
of representation of
some of the spirits

00:26:38.810 --> 00:26:42.160 align:middle line:90%
we're going to bring back for--

00:26:42.160 --> 00:26:44.800 align:middle line:84%
just representation of all
the different entities.

00:26:44.800 --> 00:26:47.298 align:middle line:84%
So if-- the more we could
really picture them, the better.

00:26:47.298 --> 00:26:48.840 align:middle line:84%
So if you need to
stare at something,

00:26:48.840 --> 00:26:51.007 align:middle line:84%
or whether it's upside down
or the different things,

00:26:51.007 --> 00:26:52.290 align:middle line:90%
go for it.

00:26:52.290 --> 00:26:55.410 align:middle line:84%
Plus, we have different-- there
may be other modes besides

00:26:55.410 --> 00:26:58.410 align:middle line:84%
the Ouija Board that they
want to talk to us through,

00:26:58.410 --> 00:27:01.620 align:middle line:84%
like the tambourine,
or something may appear

00:27:01.620 --> 00:27:03.528 align:middle line:84%
on our camera, or
there's a radio--

00:27:03.528 --> 00:27:05.070 align:middle line:84%
because there's a
lot of music going.

00:27:05.070 --> 00:27:07.460 align:middle line:84%
You're a musician and we're
dealing with two musicians.

00:27:07.460 --> 00:27:09.990 align:middle line:84%
You might see something, a
flash in the side of your eye,

00:27:09.990 --> 00:27:12.995 align:middle line:84%
or a cold or warm air
come all over you.

00:27:12.995 --> 00:27:15.120 align:middle line:84%
Or someone who's literally
talking to you that only

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:16.369 align:middle line:90%
you can hear.

00:27:16.369 --> 00:27:17.866 align:middle line:90%
[VOCALIZING]

00:27:17.866 --> 00:27:29.732 align:middle line:90%


00:27:29.732 --> 00:27:32.190 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Can you teach people
to communicate with the dead?

00:27:32.190 --> 00:27:33.390 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I can teach people.

00:27:33.390 --> 00:27:34.885 align:middle line:90%
I think we're all born doing it.

00:27:34.885 --> 00:27:35.760 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Interesting.

00:27:35.760 --> 00:27:37.620 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: And I think
it just gets taught out

00:27:37.620 --> 00:27:39.840 align:middle line:84%
of us, especially
in Western culture,

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:42.330 align:middle line:84%
because we're so matter of
fact, even our religion isn't

00:27:42.330 --> 00:27:43.320 align:middle line:90%
that spiritual.

00:27:43.320 --> 00:27:46.150 align:middle line:84%
That's changing, but
that's your imagination.

00:27:46.150 --> 00:27:47.470 align:middle line:90%
This is real life.

00:27:47.470 --> 00:27:49.500 align:middle line:84%
But I think we're
all born with it.

00:27:49.500 --> 00:27:51.300 align:middle line:84%
And it's just-- it's
like going to the gym

00:27:51.300 --> 00:27:54.300 align:middle line:84%
and learning to work out,
to just allow that intuition

00:27:54.300 --> 00:27:55.290 align:middle line:90%
to come through.

00:27:55.290 --> 00:27:57.190 align:middle line:90%
There's exercises you can do.

00:27:57.190 --> 00:27:59.080 align:middle line:90%
There's meditations you can do.

00:27:59.080 --> 00:28:02.760 align:middle line:84%
It's really just about
shutting down your left brain.

00:28:02.760 --> 00:28:06.090 align:middle line:84%
You have to get reason
and logic out of the way

00:28:06.090 --> 00:28:08.472 align:middle line:84%
and allow that world where--
that right brain side,

00:28:08.472 --> 00:28:09.555 align:middle line:90%
where anything can happen.

00:28:09.555 --> 00:28:12.150 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: If you cannot
communicate with a loved one,

00:28:12.150 --> 00:28:13.170 align:middle line:90%
what does that mean?

00:28:13.170 --> 00:28:15.510 align:middle line:84%
Who's been blocked,
or what's happening?

00:28:15.510 --> 00:28:19.980 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Well, if you cannot,
it could be your own fear,

00:28:19.980 --> 00:28:24.240 align:middle line:84%
or your own doubt, or
your own disbelief.

00:28:24.240 --> 00:28:27.090 align:middle line:84%
I mean, sometimes they
really don't have anything

00:28:27.090 --> 00:28:28.390 align:middle line:90%
to say they don't want to.

00:28:28.390 --> 00:28:30.180 align:middle line:84%
It's rare because
they usually do.

00:28:30.180 --> 00:28:30.390 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:28:30.390 --> 00:28:32.770 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: But there is some
spiritual, like, eh, I'm done.

00:28:32.770 --> 00:28:33.570 align:middle line:90%
I've moved on.

00:28:33.570 --> 00:28:36.750 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to go back
and talk to anybody.

00:28:36.750 --> 00:28:39.410 align:middle line:84%
So I don't know that there's
a lot of blame effect to it.

00:28:39.410 --> 00:28:40.770 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Do they reincarnate?

00:28:40.770 --> 00:28:42.460 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I think, yes.

00:28:42.460 --> 00:28:44.520 align:middle line:90%
And what's crazy is that--

00:28:44.520 --> 00:28:46.740 align:middle line:84%
I believe in
reincarnation, personally.

00:28:46.740 --> 00:28:49.650 align:middle line:84%
Somebody told me who I
was a billion years ago.

00:28:49.650 --> 00:28:52.083 align:middle line:84%
And actually, for the
believer that I am,

00:28:52.083 --> 00:28:53.250 align:middle line:90%
I like to start out skeptic.

00:28:53.250 --> 00:28:55.130 align:middle line:84%
So I go, yeah, yeah,
everybody's somebody.

00:28:55.130 --> 00:28:58.800 align:middle line:84%
This was the 80s, when
everybody was Cleopatra.

00:28:58.800 --> 00:28:59.640 align:middle line:90%
But I'm like, OK.

00:28:59.640 --> 00:29:01.530 align:middle line:84%
But then again, I
found this house

00:29:01.530 --> 00:29:03.840 align:middle line:84%
without knowing the address
and it was proven later.

00:29:03.840 --> 00:29:06.605 align:middle line:84%
Everything was-- so,
OK, I'm this person.

00:29:06.605 --> 00:29:07.480 align:middle line:90%
I went in this house.

00:29:07.480 --> 00:29:08.970 align:middle line:90%
I knew every--

00:29:08.970 --> 00:29:10.500 align:middle line:90%
I believe I was this person.

00:29:10.500 --> 00:29:12.680 align:middle line:84%
Then on one day,
I'm doing a seance,

00:29:12.680 --> 00:29:13.680 align:middle line:90%
and there, she shows up.

00:29:13.680 --> 00:29:16.890 align:middle line:84%
It's like, oh, well,
there goes my th--

00:29:16.890 --> 00:29:18.690 align:middle line:84%
But again, if time
and space doesn't

00:29:18.690 --> 00:29:23.130 align:middle line:84%
exist on the other side,
I could be not completely

00:29:23.130 --> 00:29:24.490 align:middle line:90%
her reincarnation.

00:29:24.490 --> 00:29:28.530 align:middle line:84%
But aspects of, lines of,
maybe karmic things part

00:29:28.530 --> 00:29:32.370 align:middle line:84%
of that I took on in my life of
hers, and knowledge-- but she's

00:29:32.370 --> 00:29:33.520 align:middle line:90%
still there.

00:29:33.520 --> 00:29:35.760 align:middle line:84%
So even if you're
reincarnated, you can hang out.

00:29:35.760 --> 00:29:38.520 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I was going to
say, if you reincarnate,

00:29:38.520 --> 00:29:41.790 align:middle line:84%
does that mean you've lost
contact with your spirit?

00:29:41.790 --> 00:29:42.983 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I don't think so.

00:29:42.983 --> 00:29:44.400 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Or can
you still do that?

00:29:44.400 --> 00:29:44.940 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I think--

00:29:44.940 --> 00:29:45.980 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Here's an example.

00:29:45.980 --> 00:29:46.780 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: OK.

00:29:46.780 --> 00:29:50.010 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Let's say your
cousin dies and you

00:29:50.010 --> 00:29:51.930 align:middle line:84%
want to communicate
with your cousin,

00:29:51.930 --> 00:29:54.160 align:middle line:84%
but they've
reincarnated already.

00:29:54.160 --> 00:29:57.000 align:middle line:84%
Can you still get in touch
with them, or are they gone?

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:58.620 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: No, I
think that they can.

00:29:58.620 --> 00:30:00.870 align:middle line:90%
That's like that thing with my--

00:30:00.870 --> 00:30:03.420 align:middle line:90%
I think, again, essences of.

00:30:03.420 --> 00:30:06.700 align:middle line:84%
I think it's, again, too much
for my tiny little human brain.

00:30:06.700 --> 00:30:09.510 align:middle line:84%
But if we're part of this great
consciousness, whatever it is,

00:30:09.510 --> 00:30:11.220 align:middle line:84%
and that part of
their spirit goes on,

00:30:11.220 --> 00:30:15.030 align:middle line:84%
and they're now some new
person, that other part of that

00:30:15.030 --> 00:30:16.260 align:middle line:90%
was them, it's part of us.

00:30:16.260 --> 00:30:18.060 align:middle line:84%
Whether it's in our
ancestry, whether it's

00:30:18.060 --> 00:30:23.130 align:middle line:84%
in our blood, or the great
records, I think both.

00:30:23.130 --> 00:30:24.810 align:middle line:90%
It's ever-expanding.

00:30:24.810 --> 00:30:27.660 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: When you've been
conducting your seances, what

00:30:27.660 --> 00:30:30.330 align:middle line:84%
has been, for you, the most
unusual thing that's ever

00:30:30.330 --> 00:30:31.386 align:middle line:90%
happened?

00:30:31.386 --> 00:30:34.470 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: OK, I think the most
unusual thing that happened

00:30:34.470 --> 00:30:36.450 align:middle line:84%
was somebody
bursting into flames

00:30:36.450 --> 00:30:37.635 align:middle line:90%
and spontaneous combustion.

00:30:37.635 --> 00:30:39.270 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: We've got
a video of that.

00:30:39.270 --> 00:30:40.717 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Oh, OK.

00:30:40.717 --> 00:30:41.551 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES]

00:30:41.551 --> 00:30:43.500 align:middle line:10%
>>STEPHEN NORRINGTON: When I
had lived up on that street,

00:30:43.500 --> 00:30:44.300 align:middle line:10%
I knew that house.

00:30:44.300 --> 00:30:46.000 align:middle line:10%
And it was really a
weird, creepy house.

00:30:46.000 --> 00:30:49.505 align:middle line:10%
The legend about that house
were known to all the neighbors.

00:30:49.505 --> 00:30:50.880 align:middle line:10%
And one of the
first things I had

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:52.635 align:middle line:10%
when I moved in was
my new neighbors

00:30:52.635 --> 00:30:54.510 align:middle line:10%
said, hey, you know that
Astor Mansion that's

00:30:54.510 --> 00:30:55.180 align:middle line:10%
just down the road?

00:30:55.180 --> 00:30:56.150 align:middle line:10%
Loads of weird shit
happened there.

00:30:56.150 --> 00:30:57.810 align:middle line:10%
>>LAURENT MALAQUAIS: I don't
really believe in this stuff.

00:30:57.810 --> 00:31:00.292 align:middle line:10%
So to me, it was just
kind of a fun project

00:31:00.292 --> 00:31:01.750 align:middle line:10%
to do and just to
see what happens,

00:31:01.750 --> 00:31:03.210 align:middle line:10%
see if this thing would sell.

00:31:03.210 --> 00:31:06.525 align:middle line:10%
What ended up happening
is, I became a believer.

00:31:06.525 --> 00:31:08.400 align:middle line:10%
Apparently, there was
three spirits in there.

00:31:08.400 --> 00:31:10.488 align:middle line:10%
Was a really sad spirit.

00:31:10.488 --> 00:31:12.030 align:middle line:10%
There were some
other kind of spirit,

00:31:12.030 --> 00:31:14.010 align:middle line:10%
and then there was
an angry spirit.

00:31:14.010 --> 00:31:17.280 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: We got a really,
really angry spirit here,

00:31:17.280 --> 00:31:18.730 align:middle line:10%
who doesn't want us here at all.

00:31:18.730 --> 00:31:20.340 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: At one point,
they're asking the spirit,

00:31:20.340 --> 00:31:21.298 align:middle line:10%
can you give me a sign?

00:31:21.298 --> 00:31:22.800 align:middle line:10%
>> Were you young when you died?

00:31:22.800 --> 00:31:24.425 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: Do you have
a message that you

00:31:24.425 --> 00:31:25.680 align:middle line:10%
want to give to anybody here?

00:31:25.680 --> 00:31:27.055 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: And
they kept trying

00:31:27.055 --> 00:31:29.460 align:middle line:10%
to talk to the angry
spirit for some reason.

00:31:29.460 --> 00:31:32.200 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: You came in very
strongly into the room.

00:31:32.200 --> 00:31:34.630 align:middle line:10%
Do you have something
you want to say?

00:31:34.630 --> 00:31:36.900 align:middle line:10%
Hi.

00:31:36.900 --> 00:31:37.700 align:middle line:10%
[CHUCKLES]

00:31:37.700 --> 00:31:39.870 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: The
windows blew open--

00:31:39.870 --> 00:31:40.760 align:middle line:10%
OK, weird.

00:31:40.760 --> 00:31:42.515 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: It is-- he's
here and that's OK,

00:31:42.515 --> 00:31:44.890 align:middle line:10%
and we welcome him because we
want to get his story, too.

00:31:44.890 --> 00:31:46.807 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: Then the
windows blew open again.

00:31:46.807 --> 00:31:48.735 align:middle line:10%
>> [LAUGHS]

00:31:48.735 --> 00:31:50.160 align:middle line:10%


00:31:50.160 --> 00:31:52.160 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: And then the
record player started.

00:31:52.160 --> 00:31:53.140 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: Did you just
turn on the speaker?

00:31:53.140 --> 00:31:53.410 align:middle line:10%
>> Sh.

00:31:53.410 --> 00:31:54.570 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: Did you just
turn on the speakers?

00:31:54.570 --> 00:31:55.960 align:middle line:10%
>> It just went again.

00:31:55.960 --> 00:31:57.975 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: Did another
spirit turn on the speaker?

00:31:57.975 --> 00:31:59.725 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: >> And
then suddenly everyone

00:31:59.725 --> 00:32:00.852 align:middle line:10%
started staring at me.

00:32:00.852 --> 00:32:02.820 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: [VOCALIZING]

00:32:02.820 --> 00:32:03.804 align:middle line:10%


00:32:03.804 --> 00:32:05.772 align:middle line:10%
>> [SCREAMS]

00:32:05.772 --> 00:32:06.756 align:middle line:10%


00:32:06.756 --> 00:32:07.924 align:middle line:10%
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:32:07.924 --> 00:32:08.724 align:middle line:10%


00:32:08.724 --> 00:32:10.200 align:middle line:10%
[FIRE ALARM BEEPS]

00:32:10.200 --> 00:32:11.676 align:middle line:10%


00:32:11.676 --> 00:32:13.580 align:middle line:10%
>>MALAQUAIS: I was
not understanding

00:32:13.580 --> 00:32:14.662 align:middle line:10%
what was going on.

00:32:14.662 --> 00:32:15.995 align:middle line:90%
But it turned out I was on fire.

00:32:15.995 --> 00:32:16.625 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Jeez.

00:32:16.625 --> 00:32:17.405 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: [LAUGHS]

00:32:17.405 --> 00:32:18.620 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What happened to him?

00:32:18.620 --> 00:32:20.203 align:middle line:84%
Did he get too close
to the fireplace?

00:32:20.203 --> 00:32:22.850 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: No, he was nowhere
near a fireplace or a candle.

00:32:22.850 --> 00:32:25.880 align:middle line:84%
He just-- spontaneous
combustion.

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:29.090 align:middle line:84%
Like angel wings of
fire up his back.

00:32:29.090 --> 00:32:31.580 align:middle line:90%
So I shut it down.

00:32:31.580 --> 00:32:33.920 align:middle line:84%
I'm screaming, shutting
down my guards and my--

00:32:33.920 --> 00:32:35.420 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You were in shock.

00:32:35.420 --> 00:32:36.740 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: No, I'm a medic.

00:32:36.740 --> 00:32:37.730 align:middle line:90%
I'm also a med--

00:32:37.730 --> 00:32:38.940 align:middle line:90%
I've done a lot of things.

00:32:38.940 --> 00:32:41.740 align:middle line:90%
So I'm like, drop and roll!

00:32:41.740 --> 00:32:42.770 align:middle line:90%
And we got it out.

00:32:42.770 --> 00:32:44.902 align:middle line:84%
Instead of being-- but
he was inspired by it.

00:32:44.902 --> 00:32:45.860 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Was he burned?

00:32:45.860 --> 00:32:48.030 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, there was
blistering on his back.

00:32:48.030 --> 00:32:48.830 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh.

00:32:48.830 --> 00:32:51.080 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: But what is
amazing is that he's like,

00:32:51.080 --> 00:32:51.900 align:middle line:90%
no, let's go on.

00:32:51.900 --> 00:32:53.590 align:middle line:84%
So I actually talked
to the spirit.

00:32:53.590 --> 00:32:55.580 align:middle line:84%
I said, we're not even
going to get rid of you.

00:32:55.580 --> 00:32:57.920 align:middle line:84%
But three weeks later, this
beautiful man, who was just

00:32:57.920 --> 00:32:59.780 align:middle line:90%
talking, Laurent, he goes--

00:32:59.780 --> 00:33:01.430 align:middle line:90%
he showed me his back.

00:33:01.430 --> 00:33:03.290 align:middle line:84%
And it literally
looked like he had went

00:33:03.290 --> 00:33:05.170 align:middle line:90%
and got a tattoo of a dragon.

00:33:05.170 --> 00:33:05.970 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Wow.

00:33:05.970 --> 00:33:07.240 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: And on the
small of his back--

00:33:07.240 --> 00:33:08.870 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: That was
burned into his back?

00:33:08.870 --> 00:33:10.510 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: That's
exactly who I called in

00:33:10.510 --> 00:33:11.990 align:middle line:90%
to shut down the seance.

00:33:11.990 --> 00:33:13.190 align:middle line:90%
I worked dragon energy.

00:33:13.190 --> 00:33:14.690 align:middle line:90%
It's that crossroads of magic--

00:33:14.690 --> 00:33:15.800 align:middle line:90%
a good dragon.

00:33:15.800 --> 00:33:19.190 align:middle line:84%
And it was like, oh my gosh, you
have a tramp stamp of a dragon.

00:33:19.190 --> 00:33:20.210 align:middle line:90%
He was so inspiring.

00:33:20.210 --> 00:33:22.010 align:middle line:84%
Actually, that was
Stephen Norrington,

00:33:22.010 --> 00:33:23.630 align:middle line:84%
in the beginning,
the guy who wrote

00:33:23.630 --> 00:33:25.460 align:middle line:84%
"The League of
Extraordinary Gentlemen,"

00:33:25.460 --> 00:33:28.340 align:middle line:84%
and the "Blade" series, that
they were inspired to write

00:33:28.340 --> 00:33:29.750 align:middle line:90%
a whole script about this.

00:33:29.750 --> 00:33:32.400 align:middle line:90%
But yeah, that was pretty wild.

00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:37.970 align:middle line:84%
I've had some crazy things
happen, on "Ghost Adventures"

00:33:37.970 --> 00:33:39.380 align:middle line:84%
and in different
shows I've done.

00:33:39.380 --> 00:33:41.195 align:middle line:90%
But this was the wildest.

00:33:41.195 --> 00:33:43.280 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Why did you
have a Ouija Board there?

00:33:43.280 --> 00:33:44.815 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I have
used a Ouija Board

00:33:44.815 --> 00:33:45.940 align:middle line:90%
since I was seven or eight.

00:33:45.940 --> 00:33:47.148 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: No, have you really?

00:33:47.148 --> 00:33:47.948 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I have.

00:33:47.948 --> 00:33:49.385 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: They let
in bad spirits.

00:33:49.385 --> 00:33:52.520 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: Only if you let them.

00:33:52.520 --> 00:33:54.200 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I'm not sure
about that, Patti.

00:33:54.200 --> 00:33:55.450 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: See, I believe
it's like your front door.

00:33:55.450 --> 00:33:57.597 align:middle line:84%
Again, I believe this is
our realm of existence.

00:33:57.597 --> 00:33:59.930 align:middle line:84%
And you're not going to open
the front door of your home

00:33:59.930 --> 00:34:02.570 align:middle line:84%
and go, anybody come out
there, all the crazy people.

00:34:02.570 --> 00:34:04.820 align:middle line:84%
So you don't do that
with a Ouija Board.

00:34:04.820 --> 00:34:08.480 align:middle line:84%
I don't think they should
be sold in toy stores.

00:34:08.480 --> 00:34:11.120 align:middle line:84%
I don't think they should
have the same directions.

00:34:11.120 --> 00:34:11.960 align:middle line:90%
This is not a toy.

00:34:11.960 --> 00:34:12.500 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's not a game.

00:34:12.500 --> 00:34:13.460 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: This should
not be a game.

00:34:13.460 --> 00:34:14.583 align:middle line:90%
This should not be a toy.

00:34:14.583 --> 00:34:16.250 align:middle line:84%
There should not be
of a Barbie version.

00:34:16.250 --> 00:34:18.530 align:middle line:90%
I have the Barbie version, too.

00:34:18.530 --> 00:34:20.870 align:middle line:90%
But I've literally had--

00:34:20.870 --> 00:34:22.790 align:middle line:84%
I have dozens of
them and I've never

00:34:22.790 --> 00:34:24.380 align:middle line:84%
had a bad experience
with one ever,

00:34:24.380 --> 00:34:25.765 align:middle line:90%
because that is not my intent.

00:34:25.765 --> 00:34:27.230 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: God, I
had a horrible one.

00:34:27.230 --> 00:34:29.400 align:middle line:84%
When I was doing my
local show in St. Louis

00:34:29.400 --> 00:34:34.310 align:middle line:84%
years ago, back in 1996, I had
a Ouija Board in the studio

00:34:34.310 --> 00:34:37.280 align:middle line:84%
because I was doing a
little show on Ouija Boards.

00:34:37.280 --> 00:34:39.889 align:middle line:84%
Everything went wrong in
the studio technically

00:34:39.889 --> 00:34:41.060 align:middle line:90%
you can imagine.

00:34:41.060 --> 00:34:42.739 align:middle line:90%
It never went wrong.

00:34:42.739 --> 00:34:45.020 align:middle line:84%
But this time,
everything went wrong.

00:34:45.020 --> 00:34:46.159 align:middle line:90%
The board wouldn't work.

00:34:46.159 --> 00:34:47.929 align:middle line:90%
The commercials wouldn't run.

00:34:47.929 --> 00:34:51.469 align:middle line:84%
I finally gave it to my producer
and said, take this and get it

00:34:51.469 --> 00:34:53.239 align:middle line:90%
out of here, so he did.

00:34:53.239 --> 00:34:55.889 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't know what he
did with it at the time.

00:34:55.889 --> 00:34:59.370 align:middle line:84%
And then all of a sudden, I
had met one of our newscasters,

00:34:59.370 --> 00:35:00.825 align:middle line:90%
his name was Darryl.

00:35:00.825 --> 00:35:04.610 align:middle line:84%
A week later, Darryl had
been fired from our place,

00:35:04.610 --> 00:35:07.390 align:middle line:90%
for our station.

00:35:07.390 --> 00:35:08.640 align:middle line:90%
And I said, how are you doing?

00:35:08.640 --> 00:35:09.680 align:middle line:90%
He said, not well.

00:35:09.680 --> 00:35:11.030 align:middle line:90%
I said, what do you mean?

00:35:11.030 --> 00:35:14.480 align:middle line:84%
He said, I got fired,
George, a week ago.

00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:15.620 align:middle line:90%
You didn't know about that?

00:35:15.620 --> 00:35:18.080 align:middle line:84%
And my relationship
fell down the tubes.

00:35:18.080 --> 00:35:19.700 align:middle line:90%
Everything is wrong.

00:35:19.700 --> 00:35:22.970 align:middle line:84%
And he said, but at least I
have that gift you gave me.

00:35:22.970 --> 00:35:25.340 align:middle line:90%
And I said, what gift?

00:35:25.340 --> 00:35:29.650 align:middle line:84%
He said, Howard gave
me the Ouija Board.

00:35:29.650 --> 00:35:31.600 align:middle line:90%
I said, do you still have it?

00:35:31.600 --> 00:35:32.440 align:middle line:90%
And he said, yeah.

00:35:32.440 --> 00:35:35.300 align:middle line:90%
I said, Darryl, get rid of it.

00:35:35.300 --> 00:35:39.490 align:middle line:84%
And he did and he got
rehired, and everything

00:35:39.490 --> 00:35:41.570 align:middle line:90%
started working for him again.

00:35:41.570 --> 00:35:42.860 align:middle line:90%
I don't like them, Patti.

00:35:42.860 --> 00:35:43.660 align:middle line:90%
I don't like them.

00:35:43.660 --> 00:35:44.493 align:middle line:90%
>>NEGRI: I get that.

00:35:44.493 --> 00:35:47.050 align:middle line:84%
But see, that was a
bad one, or else we--

00:35:47.050 --> 00:35:49.060 align:middle line:90%
humans, or whatever, a spirit--

00:35:49.060 --> 00:35:50.330 align:middle line:90%
that became a bad thing.

00:35:50.330 --> 00:35:52.990 align:middle line:84%
Again, we give the power
to things by our intention,

00:35:52.990 --> 00:35:54.010 align:middle line:90%
I believe.

00:35:54.010 --> 00:35:55.660 align:middle line:90%
So I haven't had a bad one.

00:35:55.660 --> 00:35:58.030 align:middle line:90%
And again, I'm intending not to.

00:35:58.030 --> 00:35:59.390 align:middle line:90%
But yes, get rid of it.

00:35:59.390 --> 00:36:00.910 align:middle line:84%
I've had people
show up at my house.

00:36:00.910 --> 00:36:03.430 align:middle line:84%
I had done a music
video, or somebody,

00:36:03.430 --> 00:36:06.838 align:middle line:84%
and we hadn't even
used a Ouija Board.

00:36:06.838 --> 00:36:09.130 align:middle line:84%
One day, all of a sudden, a
crew member, the camera man

00:36:09.130 --> 00:36:13.060 align:middle line:84%
was at my front door, handing
me this beautiful plywood

00:36:13.060 --> 00:36:14.352 align:middle line:90%
board from 1921, a Ouija Board.

00:36:14.352 --> 00:36:15.518 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Mm, classic, right?

00:36:15.518 --> 00:36:18.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, classic, and it
had all sorts of weird symbols.

00:36:18.300 --> 00:36:19.610 align:middle line:90%
He goes, will you take this?

00:36:19.610 --> 00:36:20.817 align:middle line:90%
I'm like, sure.

00:36:20.817 --> 00:36:22.400 align:middle line:84%
He wouldn't give me
the history of it.

00:36:22.400 --> 00:36:23.405 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He didn't
want it either.

00:36:23.405 --> 00:36:25.520 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: But again, I
think we're stronger.

00:36:25.520 --> 00:36:27.460 align:middle line:84%
So if there's anything
bad, I get it out.

00:36:27.460 --> 00:36:29.410 align:middle line:90%
I have this haunted doll that--

00:36:29.410 --> 00:36:31.420 align:middle line:84%
the girl who sent it
to me from Belgium,

00:36:31.420 --> 00:36:33.200 align:middle line:84%
it made her hair fall
out for three years.

00:36:33.200 --> 00:36:34.000 align:middle line:90%
It made her sick.

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:34.210 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh my god.

00:36:34.210 --> 00:36:35.668 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: But I got
that spirit out.

00:36:35.668 --> 00:36:37.553 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I didn't--
working with my guys.

00:36:37.553 --> 00:36:39.220 align:middle line:84%
And now I have a
beautiful haunted doll.

00:36:39.220 --> 00:36:40.140 align:middle line:90%
It just has a nice little--

00:36:40.140 --> 00:36:41.650 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Have you heard of
Robert, the haunted doll, down

00:36:41.650 --> 00:36:42.115 align:middle line:90%
in Florida?

00:36:42.115 --> 00:36:43.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Oh, yeah,
Robert the haunted doll.

00:36:43.320 --> 00:36:45.050 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: A lot of people
have had horrible experiences

00:36:45.050 --> 00:36:45.850 align:middle line:90%
with him.

00:36:45.850 --> 00:36:47.670 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Peggy the
doll, in Zak's museum--

00:36:47.670 --> 00:36:49.670 align:middle line:84%
I did a seance with Peggy,
my first doll seance.

00:36:49.670 --> 00:36:50.950 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: They go
running around at night.

00:36:50.950 --> 00:36:52.783 align:middle line:84%
You can hear their
footsteps, pitter-patter.

00:36:52.783 --> 00:36:54.880 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: Yeah, my
doll runs around

00:36:54.880 --> 00:36:55.990 align:middle line:90%
in the night a little bit.

00:36:55.990 --> 00:36:56.980 align:middle line:90%
You can see her eyes move.

00:36:56.980 --> 00:36:59.350 align:middle line:10%
They don't-- somebody will
do a photoshoot and she'll be

00:36:59.350 --> 00:36:59.950 align:middle line:10%
in the background.

00:36:59.950 --> 00:37:01.080 align:middle line:10%
She'll look different in every--

00:37:01.080 --> 00:37:01.960 align:middle line:10%
I love haunted dolls.

00:37:01.960 --> 00:37:03.627 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What's the
future hold for you?

00:37:03.627 --> 00:37:05.972 align:middle line:90%
What's next for you?

00:37:05.972 --> 00:37:08.483 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I think I have to
keep writing a little bit

00:37:08.483 --> 00:37:10.650 align:middle line:84%
because again, I've had
such success with this book.

00:37:10.650 --> 00:37:11.880 align:middle line:90%
And maybe I should do a--

00:37:11.880 --> 00:37:13.920 align:middle line:84%
because I call this
a baby book, so I

00:37:13.920 --> 00:37:15.300 align:middle line:90%
need to do a little bit more.

00:37:15.300 --> 00:37:17.280 align:middle line:90%
I still want to do more TV.

00:37:17.280 --> 00:37:19.590 align:middle line:90%
Because a bigger platform--

00:37:19.590 --> 00:37:22.140 align:middle line:84%
again, because it's all about
empowerment, not me or what I

00:37:22.140 --> 00:37:23.010 align:middle line:90%
do.

00:37:23.010 --> 00:37:24.122 align:middle line:90%
People are so fabulous.

00:37:24.122 --> 00:37:25.080 align:middle line:90%
They have to know that.

00:37:25.080 --> 00:37:26.740 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, you had fun
with "Ghost Adventures."

00:37:26.740 --> 00:37:27.960 align:middle line:84%
>>NEGRI: I love
"Ghost Adventures."

00:37:27.960 --> 00:37:29.370 align:middle line:90%
I love working with the boys.

00:37:29.370 --> 00:37:31.430 align:middle line:84%
And this last-- not
the one I just shot,

00:37:31.430 --> 00:37:32.850 align:middle line:90%
but the one that just aired--

00:37:32.850 --> 00:37:34.710 align:middle line:84%
this is the first
time Zak let me

00:37:34.710 --> 00:37:36.380 align:middle line:90%
do a house clearing on camera.

00:37:36.380 --> 00:37:38.380 align:middle line:10%
Because that doesn't fit
the style of the show--

00:37:38.380 --> 00:37:39.780 align:middle line:10%
it's these big guys
that come in and--

00:37:39.780 --> 00:37:40.570 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: Right, tough guys.

00:37:40.570 --> 00:37:41.700 align:middle line:10%
>>NEGRI: --and goes away.

00:37:41.700 --> 00:37:43.260 align:middle line:10%
But this time, he's like--

00:37:43.260 --> 00:37:46.620 align:middle line:10%
and after they're lock down and
everything, go in to clear it.

